tip.text: Such a refreshing place in the terminal, music and art softens the place and the staff is high class. Robert is a great guy! The food is nice as well! Forgot for a moment that we were traveling.
It's clean, sharp and run by good people. And the Dimattina coffee from Melbourne tastes good as cold brew or espresso!
